Package: kfigr
Title: Integrated chunk anchoring and referencing for knitr documents.
Version: 1.0.2
Date: 2015-01-16
Author: Michael Koohafkan
Maintainer: Michael Koohafkan <michael.koohafkan@gmail.com>
Description: kfigr is a streamlined cross-referencing system for R markdown documents that integrates with knitr. The package defines a hook for anchoring code chunks and the ability to track and cross-reference chunks that produce document elements such as figures, tables and code blocks.
Depends: R (>= 3.1.0)
Imports: knitr (>= 1.6)
Suggests: ggplot2
LazyData: true
VignetteBuilder: knitr
License: GPL-2
